== Events == * {{ill|Empress Kōgyoku|ja|皇極天皇}} 2 ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|643|ja|643年}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日}}) – {{ill|Soga no Emishi|ja|蘇我蝦夷}} arbitrarily grants the {{ill|purple cap|ja|紫冠}} to his son, {{ill|Soga no Iruka|ja|蘇我入鹿}}, making him Minister. * {{ill|Jishō (era)|ja|治承}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1180|ja|1180年}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日}}) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝}}, having fled to {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国}}, enters {{ill|Kamakura|ja|鎌倉}} with the assistance of {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤}} and others. * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保}} 13 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842年}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|江戸幕府}} appoints {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳}} to oversee hydraulic and civil engineering surveys of the {{ill|Tone River|ja|利根川}}. == Births == * {{ill|Qianlong Emperor|ja|乾隆}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1760|ja|1760年}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日}}) – {{ill|Jiaqing Emperor|ja|嘉慶帝}}, 7th Emperor of the {{ill|Qing dynasty|ja|清}} (+ {{ill|1820|ja|1820年}}). * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1831|ja|1831年}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日}}) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平}}, 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1866|ja|1866年}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日}}) – {{ill|Sun Yat-sen|ja|孫文}}, revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統}} (+ {{ill|1925|ja|1925年}}). == Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō (Japan)|ja|天正}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1584|ja|1584年}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日}}) – {{ill|Ashina Moritaka|ja|蘆名盛隆}}, {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名}} (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561年}}). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1715|ja|1715年}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日}}) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海}}, also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲}}, astronomer and calendrical scholar (* {{ill|1639|ja|1639年}}). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|延享}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747年}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日}}) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行}}, one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士}} (* {{ill|1665|ja|1665年}}). == Commemorations == [[Category:Japanese historical events]] [[Category:Edo period]] [[Category:Shogunate officials]] [[Category:Sengoku period]] [[Category:Samurai]] [[Category:Republic of China]] [[Category:Translated pages]] [[ja:蘇我入鹿の紫冠授与]] == See Also == {{Lunar Calendar See Also|10|5|10|7|9|6|11|10|1006}} [[Category:Lunar Calendar Days]] [[sn:October 6 (Old Lunar Calendar)]][[ko:음력 10월 6일]] [[ja:10月6日 (旧暦)]] [[Category:Lunar Calendar Days]] [[sn:October 6 (Old Lunar Calendar)]][[ko:음력 10월 6일]] [[Category:Lunar October]] [[Category:Lunar_Calendar_Days]][[sn:October 6 (Old Lunar Calendar)]][[Category:Lunar_Calendar_Days]]
