qq-October 6 (Lunisolar)-qq {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Empress Kōgyoku|ja|皇極天皇|qq=}} 2 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|643|ja|643rd year|qq=}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Emishi|ja|蘇我Ezo|qq=}} arbitrarily grants the {{ill|purple cap|ja|紫冠|qq=}} to his son, {{ill|Soga no Iruka|ja|蘇我入鹿|qq=}} , making him Minister. * {{ill|Jishō (era)|ja|治承|qq=}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=}} , having fled to {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|qq=}} , enters {{ill|Kamakura|ja|鎌倉|qq=}} with the assistance of {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=}} and others. * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=}} 13 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} appoints {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=}} to oversee hydraulic and civil engineering surveys of the {{ill|Tone River|ja|利根川|qq=}} . == Births == * {{ill|Qianlong Emperor|ja|乾隆|qq=}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1760|ja|1760th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Jiaqing Emperor|ja|嘉慶帝|qq=}} , 7th Emperor of the {{ill|Qing dynasty|ja|清|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1820|ja|1820th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1831|ja|1831st year|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平|qq=}} , 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人|qq=}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1866|ja|1866th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Sun Yat-sen|ja|孫文|qq=}} , revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1925|ja|1925th year|qq=}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō (Japan)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1584|ja|1584th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashina Moritaka|ja|蘆名盛隆|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|qq=}} (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1715|ja|1715th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=}} , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|qq=}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* {{ill|1639|ja|1639th year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|qq=}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|qq=}} (* {{ill|1665|ja|1665th year|qq=}} ). == Commemorations ==
