{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 6일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Empress Kōgyoku|ja|皇極天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|643|ja|643rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Emishi|ja|蘇我Ezo|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} arbitrarily grants the {{ill|purple cap|ja|紫冠|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to his son, {{ill|Soga no Iruka|ja|蘇我入鹿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , making him Minister. * {{ill|Jishō (era)|ja|治承|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , having fled to {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , enters {{ill|Kamakura|ja|鎌倉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} with the assistance of {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and others. * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 13 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} appoints {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} to oversee hydraulic and civil engineering surveys of the {{ill|Tone River|ja|利根川|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . == Births == * {{ill|Qianlong Emperor|ja|乾隆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1760|ja|1760th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Jiaqing Emperor|ja|嘉慶帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 7th Emperor of the {{ill|Qing dynasty|ja|清|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1820|ja|1820th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1831|ja|1831st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1866|ja|1866th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Sun Yat-sen|ja|孫文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1925|ja|1925th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō (Japan)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1584|ja|1584th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ashina Moritaka|ja|蘆名盛隆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1715|ja|1715th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* {{ill|1639|ja|1639th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1665|ja|1665th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). == Commemorations ==
