== Events == * {{ill|Empress Kōgyoku|ja|皇極天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Kōgyoku|qq=}} 2 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|643|ja|643rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/643|qq=}} {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 22|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Soga no Emishi|ja|蘇我Ezo|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga no Emishi|qq=}} arbitrarily grants the {{ill|purple cap|ja|紫冠|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/purple cap|qq=}} to his son, {{ill|Soga no Iruka|ja|蘇我入鹿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga no Iruka|qq=}} , making him Minister. * {{ill|Jishō (era)|ja|治承|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jishō (era)|qq=}} 4 (Julian {{ill|1180|ja|1180th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1180|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 26|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoritomo|qq=}} , having fled to {{ill|Awa Province|ja|安房国|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Awa Province|qq=}} , enters {{ill|Kamakura|ja|鎌倉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamakura|qq=}} with the assistance of {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Tsunetane|qq=}} and others. * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō (era)|qq=}} 13 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1842|ja|1842nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1842|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 8|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} appoints {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ninomiya Sontoku|qq=}} to oversee hydraulic and civil engineering surveys of the {{ill|Tone River|ja|利根川|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tone River|qq=}} . == Births == * {{ill|Qianlong Emperor|ja|乾隆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qianlong Emperor|qq=}} 10 (Gregorian {{ill|1760|ja|1760th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1760|qq=}} {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 13|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Jiaqing Emperor|ja|嘉慶帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jiaqing Emperor|qq=}} , 7th Emperor of the {{ill|Qing dynasty|ja|清|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qing dynasty|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1820|ja|1820th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1820|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenpō (era)|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō (era)|qq=}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1831|ja|1831st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1831|qq=}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 9|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ono Gohei|qq=}} , 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meijin (shogi)|qq=}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tongzhi Emperor|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1866|ja|1866th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1866|qq=}} {{ill|November 12|ja|11月12日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 12|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Sun Yat-sen|ja|孫文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sun Yat-sen|qq=}} , revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Provisional President of the Republic of China|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1925|ja|1925th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1925|qq=}} ). == Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō (Japan)|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Japan)|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 12 (Gregorian {{ill|1584|ja|1584th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1584|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 8|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ashina Moritaka|ja|蘆名盛隆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ashina Moritaka|qq=}} , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyo|qq=}} (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1561|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōtoku (era)|ja|正徳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōtoku (era)|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1715|ja|1715th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1715|qq=}} {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 1|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shibukawa Harumi|qq=}} , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Santetsu|qq=}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* {{ill|1639|ja|1639th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1639|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō (Japan)|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1747|qq=}} {{ill|November 8|ja|11月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 8|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Terazaka Nobuyuki|qq=}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Forty-seven rōnin|qq=}} (* {{ill|1665|ja|1665th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1665|qq=}} ). == Commemorations ==
