{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 6일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Empress Kōgyoku|ja|皇極天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Empress Kōgyoku|qq=}} 2 ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:643|643]] [[:en:November 22|November 22]] ) – {{ill|Soga no Emishi|ja|蘇我Ezo|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Soga no Emishi|qq=}} arbitrarily grants the {{ill|purple cap|ja|紫冠|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/purple cap|qq=}} to his son, [[:en:Soga no Iruka|Soga no Iruka]] , making him Minister. * [[:en:Jishō|Jishō (era)]] 4 (Julian [[:en:1180|1180]] [[:en:October 26|October 26]] ) – [[:en:Minamoto no Yoritomo|Minamoto no Yoritomo]] , having fled to [[:en:Awa Province (Chiba)|Awa Province]] , enters {{ill|Kamakura|ja|鎌倉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamakura|qq=}} with the assistance of {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Tsunetane|qq=}} and others. * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō (era)]] 13 ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1842|1842]] [[:en:November 8|November 8]] ) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} appoints [[:en:Ninomiya Sontoku|Ninomiya Sontoku]] to oversee hydraulic and civil engineering surveys of the [[:en:Tone River|Tone River]] . == Births == * {{ill|Qianlong Emperor|ja|乾隆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qianlong Emperor|qq=}} 10 (Gregorian [[:en:1760|1760]] [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ) – [[:en:Jiaqing Emperor|Jiaqing Emperor]] , 7th Emperor of the [[:en:Qing dynasty|Qing dynasty]] (+ [[:en:1820|1820]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō (era)]] 2 (Gregorian [[:en:1831|1831]] [[:en:November 9|November 9]] ) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ono Gohei|qq=}} , 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meijin (shogi)|qq=}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tongzhi Emperor|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian [[:en:1866|1866]] [[:en:November 12|November 12]] ) – [[:en:Sun Yat-sen|Sun Yat-sen]] , revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Provisional President of the Republic of China|qq=}} (+ [[:en:1925|1925]] ). == Deaths == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 12 (Gregorian [[:en:1584|1584]] [[:en:November 8|November 8]] ) – [[:en:Ashina Moritaka|Ashina Moritaka]] , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyo|qq=}} (* [[:en:1561|1561]] ). * [[:en:正德|Shōtoku (era)]] 5 (Gregorian [[:en:1715|1715]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ) – [[:en:Shibukawa Shunkai|Shibukawa Harumi]] , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Santetsu|qq=}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* [[:en:1639|1639]] ). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō (Japan)|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian [[:en:1747|1747]] [[:en:November 8|November 8]] ) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Terazaka Nobuyuki|qq=}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Forty-seven rōnin|qq=}} (* [[:en:1665|1665]] ). == Commemorations ==
