 10 (Gregorian [[:en:1760|1760]] [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ) – [[:en:Jiaqing Emperor|Jiaqing Emperor]] , 7th Emperor of the [[:en:Qing dynasty|Qing dynasty]] (+ [[:en:1820|1820]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō (era)]] 2 (Gregorian [[:en:1831|1831]] [[:en:November 9|November 9]] ) – {{ill|Ono Gohei|ja|小野五平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ono Gohei|qq=|1=Gohei Ono|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11463910}} , 12th {{ill|Meijin (shogi)|ja|名人|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meijin (shogi)|qq=|1=Meijin (shogi)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q13583292}} in shogi. * {{ill|Tongzhi Emperor|ja|同治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tongzhi Emperor|qq=|1=Tongzhi Era|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1135837}} 5 (Gregorian [[:en:1866|1866]] [[:en:November 12|November 12]] ) – [[:en:Sun Yat-sen|Sun Yat-sen]] , revolutionary and first {{ill|Provisional President of the Republic of China|ja|中華民国大総統|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Provisional President of the Republic of China|qq=|1=Great President of the Republic of China|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q837221}} (+ [[:en:1925|1925]] ). == Deaths == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 12 (Gregorian [[:en:1584|1584]] [[:en:November 8|November 8]] ) – [[:en:Ashina Moritaka|Ashina Moritaka]] , {{ill|Sengoku daimyo|ja|戦国大名|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sengoku daimyo|qq=|1=Sengoku daimyo|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q5384684}} (* [[:en:1561|1561]] ). * [[:en:正德|Shōtoku (era)]] 5 (Gregorian [[:en:1715|1715]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ) – [[:en:Shibukawa Shunkai|Shibukawa Harumi]] , also known as the 2nd {{ill|Yasui Santetsu|ja|安井算哲|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Santetsu|qq=|1=Yasui Santetsu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11450234}} , astronomer and calendrical scholar (* [[:en:1639|1639]] ). * {{ill|Enkyō (Japan)|ja|Enkyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō (Japan)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 4 (Gregorian [[:en:1747|1747]] [[:en:November 8|November 8]] ) – {{ill|Terazaka Nobuyuki|ja|寺坂信行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Terazaka Nobuyuki|qq=|1=Terasaka Kichiemon|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11457748}} , one of the {{ill|Forty-seven rōnin|ja|赤穂浪士|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Forty-seven rōnin|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 赤穂事件の人物一覧|1=Forty-seven Ronin|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q3136847}} (* [[:en:1665|1665]] ). == Commemorations ==
